DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"FXY"}, 'Reporting Currency'[Reporting Currency Code])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    TREATAS({TRUE}, 'Shop'[Is Store Retail])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Date'[Year])),
      AND('Date'[Year] IN {2019}, 'Date'[Year] IN {2018,
        2017,
        2019})
    )

EVALUATE
  TOPN(
    101,
    CALCULATETABLE(
      SUMMARIZE(VALUES('Date'), 'Date'[Month], 'Date'[Month Of Year]),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable2),
      KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable3)
    ),
    'Date'[Month Of Year],
    1,
    'Date'[Month],
    1
  )

ORDER BY
  'Date'[Month Of Year], 'Date'[Month]
